videos.description: Izaiah Brockington gets inside and uses his left hand to score the lay-in for Penn State.

videos.description: Anthony Cowan Jr. throws the ball away and Jamari Wheeler is rewarded with a layup off the pass from Myreon Jones.

videos.description: Penn State inbounds the ball with 0.6 seconds on the clock, and Myreon Jones is able to hit the 3-pointer as time expires in the half.
